## SYNCHRONIZATION SCRIPTS

### sync.bat (Windows)
```batch
@echo off
echo ========================================
echo   SYNCHRONIZATION WITH GITHUB
echo ========================================
echo.
echo 1. Checking repository status...
git status --short

echo.
